crates/arawn-engine/src/hooks/config.rs.doc_comment:
Top-level hook configuration: maps event types to lists of hook groups.

Deserialized from the `hooks` key in settings.json:
```json
{
"hooks": {
"PreToolUse": [{ "matcher": "Bash", "hooks": [{ "type": "command", "command": "..." }] }],
"SessionStart": [{ "hooks": [{ "type": "command", "command": "..." }] }]
}
}
```

A group of hooks sharing a common matcher.

```json
{
"matcher": "Bash|Edit",
"hooks": [
{ "type": "command", "command": "echo checking", "timeout": 5 }
]
}
```

crates/arawn-engine/src/hooks/loader.rs.doc_comment:
Wrapper for the hooks section in settings.json.

```json
{
"hooks": {
"PreToolUse": [ ... ],
"SessionStart": [ ... ]
}
}
```

crates/arawn-engine/src/plugins/settings.doc_comment:
Plugin settings section from `.arawn/settings.json`.

```json
{
"enabledPlugins": {
"metis@colliery-io-metis": true,
"unwanted@some-market": false
},
"pluginConfigs": {
"my-plugin": {
"options": { "API_KEY": "abc123" }
}
}
}
```
